# Feature: Put and patch Api

# Scenario: Put Api
# Given i upadte a person details with the whole user details
# Then the whole user details must be updated
# And Status code 203 must be returned


# Scenario: Patch Api
# Given i upadte a person surname within the whole user details
# Then the surname must be updated and all other detail must remain same
# And Status code 203 must be returned